<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1933-01-30T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1933-01-30T00:00:00-05:00" n="682" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d682">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">800.51W89 Czechoslovakia/204.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Czechoslovak Minister</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Veverka</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <p>I have been instructed by the Czechoslovak Government to express its
                            gratification for the invitation to discuss the problem of the
                            Czechoslovak debt as suggested in your <hi rend="italic">aide-mémoire.</hi><note n="53" xml:id="d682fn53">
                                <hi rend="italic">Supra.</hi>
                            </note>
                        </p>
                        <p>The Czechoslovak representative to the United States will be at the
                            disposal of the United States Government whenever the beginning of such
                            negotiations will be deemed advisable.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <dateline rendition="#left">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                                </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-01-30">January
                                    30, 1933</date>.</dateline>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>